title.rendered: Carol Chen Presented FW FLORESCENCE Collection for Paris Fashion Week 2022

content.rendered:
Carol Chen presented Fall/Winter 2022 "FLORESCENCE" collection for Paris Fashion Week 2022 powered by Fashion Division. Carol Chens FW 2022 Collection entitled FLORESCENCE was inspired by Singapores Gardens by the Bay, depicting a futuristic world in bloom and the hope of a brighter post-pandemic future as the city opens up again.


By Fashion-editor : Christina V Henningstad  Production: Fashionview
